dnetw:
- use a shm to communicate to monitoring apps.
- improve % reading accuracy.
- support SMP.
- support for dnetc options.
- support other Unix system (FreeBSD, ...)
- chdir in dnetc dir (so dnetw can be launch from any dir

gtkrellm plugin:
- support SMP.
- add a led for active/inactive state (as in gtkrelmms).
- left button start dnet client (configurable command line)
